description: The face of an analog clock displaying the time as eleven-thirty.
apple_vendor_description: The clock emoji showing 11:30 on Apple devices is rendered with a classic analog face, featuring a crisp white dial and bold black numerals. Subtle 3D shading and realistic lighting on Apple's design give the hands a palpable sense of depth, as if they're casting a faint shadow. This precise time often signifies a specific appointment, a moment of anticipation, or a reminder of a scheduled event communicated digitally.
